1) | Bound (T1) |\n|-----------|-------------------|-------------------|---------------|-----------------|-----------------|------------|\n| `aiter::_flash_attn_forward` | 0.35 | 0.78 | 1 / 3 | 0.43 | — | — |\n\n*Trace 2 Time (ms)* = `lca_total_kernel_time_trace2_us / 1000`. *Difference (ms)* = `delta_us (trace2 - trace1) / 1000`.\n\n## Recommendations\n\n<!-- no-actionable-findings -->\n\nNo actionable optimization opportunities identified for this category.\n\n## Detailed Analysis\n\n<!-- no-actionable-findings -->\n\nAnalysis completed successfully. Comparative screening excludes SDPA-forward operations where Trace 1 GPU kernel time is already lower than paired Trace 2 sums for this category. Flash attention is already in use on Trace 1. Improving throughput on Trace 2 falls outside Trace-1 category tuning for this comparative run.\n","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":38,"fileSize":2495,"path":"/home/AMD/khoffmey/dev/TraceLens/evals/unit_tests_comparative/test03_attention_fused_vs_unfused/analysis_output_ref/category_findings/sdpa_fwd_findings.md","readRange":{"startLine":1,"endLine":38},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}}},"model_call_id":"bceb446c-1179-47ab-bbda-7a26ef54f842-50-zdqw","session_id":"3db865e0-9337-4698-8a24-8ac919518bc9","timestamp_ms":1777504824480}
